018_testing_0:
SELECT min(i_item_id),
       min(ca_country),
       min(ca_state),
       min(ca_county),
       min(cs_quantity),
       min(cs_list_price),
       min(cs_coupon_amt),
       min(cs_sales_price),
       min(cs_net_profit),
       min(c_birth_year),
       min(cd_dep_count)
 FROM catalog_sales,
     customer_demographics,
     customer,
     customer_address,
     date_dim,
     item

  AND c_birth_month = 10
  AND ca_state in ('IN', 'ND', 'IN')

  AND i_category = 'Books' ;
